            0.206612,
            0.117018
          ],
          "reading_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p6_b4",
          "block_type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Expectations for the improvement in performance of corporations are\nrising as the government unveiled a \"value-up\" program that will\ntarget underperformers in the stock market. Investors are\nincreasingly focused on acquiring stocks with a low price-to-book\nratio (PBR), in anticipation of them rebounding.",
          "bbox": [
            0.244101,
            0.324528,
            0.520498,
            0.070444
          ],
          "reading_order": 4
        },
        {
